properties.name: The Old Green Tree
properties.description: Posted by I0iThe Old Green Tree is the very best pub in the UK. The walls are clad in real oak panels, the seats are hard and wooden, there are real pictures of Spitfires on the wall, there are real books to pick up and read, there are real ales for sale. It is great. Having said that, if you are a foreign tourist visiting Bath, DO NOT GO TO THE OLD GREEN TREE. If you must, don\'t ask people at the top of your silly voice; "So, which of these funny warm beers do you recommend?", "Excuse me, can I take up ALL of the tables in this tiny room with my fat ass and tweny shopping bads full of touristy keepsakes?".
